org.gephi.ui.tools.plugin.edit

Class EditEdges

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.beans.FeatureDescriptor
      • org.openide.nodes.Node
        • org.openide.nodes.AbstractNode
          • org.gephi.ui.tools.plugin.edit.EditEdges
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.openide.util.HelpCtx.Provider, org.openide.util.Lookup.Provider

    public class EditEdges
extends org.openide.nodes.AbstractNode
    PropertySheet that allows to edit one or more edges. If multiple node edition mode is used at first all values will be shown as blank but will change with the editions and all edges will be set the values that the user inputs.
    Author:
    Mathieu Bastian
